PrecisOrder fixing the days upon which certain provisions of the Public Service Reform Act, being chapter 54 of the Statutes of Canada, 1992, shall COME INTO FORCE. ---------- APRIL 1, 1993 - sections 1, 2(2) and (4), 3, 4, 8 to 10, 18 {as it relates to the repeal and the substitution of s. 28 of the Public Service Employment Act}, 19, 22, 25 to 27, 29, 31, 32(1) {as it relates to the repeal of the definition "occupational category" in s. 2 of the Public Service Staff Relations Act}, 41, 74(4), 75, 76, 91, and 100 to 104; ---------- JUNE 1, 1993 - sections 2(1) and (3), 5 to 7, 11 to 17, 18 {as it relates to the repeal of s. 27 of the Public Service Employment Act}, 20, 21, 23, 24, 30, 32(1) {as it relates to the repeal of the definitions "designated employee" and "person employed in a managerial or confidential capacity" in s. 2 of the Public Service Staff Relations Act}, 32(2) to (5), 33 to 40, 42 to 73, 74(1) to (3), 77 to 81, 89, 90, 92 to 99, and 105 to 107, ---------- SEPTEMBER 1, 1993 - section 28. .
RegistrationRegistration: SI / 1993-0058 Publication Date: 1993-04-21

Order fixing the days upon which certain provisions of the Public Service
Reform Act, being chapter 54 of the Statutes of Canada, 1992, shall
COME INTO FORCE.
                                ----------
APRIL 1, 1993 - sections 1, 2(2) and (4), 3, 4, 8 to 10, 18 {as it
relates to the repeal and the substitution of s. 28 of the Public Service
Employment Act}, 19, 22, 25 to 27, 29, 31, 32(1) {as it relates to the
repeal of the definition "occupational category" in s. 2 of the Public
Service Staff Relations Act}, 41, 74(4), 75, 76, 91, and 100 to 104;
                                ----------
JUNE 1, 1993 - sections 2(1) and (3), 5 to 7, 11 to 17, 18 {as it relates
to the repeal of s. 27 of the Public Service Employment Act}, 20, 21, 23,
24, 30, 32(1) {as it relates to the repeal of the definitions "designated
employee" and "person employed in a managerial or confidential capacity" in
s. 2 of the Public Service Staff Relations Act}, 32(2) to (5), 33 to 40,
42 to 73, 74(1) to (3), 77 to 81, 89, 90, 92 to 99, and 105 to 107,
                                ----------
SEPTEMBER 1, 1993 - section 28.
.
